From 70d41b3141dcb20f0caee94c08e82d27968e114e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Sushant Butta <sbutta@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Wed, 25 Jun 2025 00:26:50 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 07/10] UPSTREAM: DP: wifi: ath12k: Adapt to new filter
 framework model

Currently, in the ath12k driver, filter pass (fp) and
monitor other (mo) filters are configured statically
for all types.

Adapt to the newer model of type, subtype based
dynamic configuration.

Patch-dependency:
	0405-0006-UPSTREAM-DP-wifi-ath12k-Add-type-subtype-support-for.patch

Signed-off-by: Sushant Butta <sbutta@qti.qualcomm.com>
